WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
When someone may be medically unsafe, the next step can be medical assessment.

00:03.000 --> 00:06.000
A clear pathway helps connect GP, hospital, mental health and eating disorder support.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
Care coordinators can help families and clinicians work out who to contact next.

00:09.000 --> 00:12.000
Open the free Eating Disorder Care Pathway Navigator.
